      <title>最新民意调查显示，腐败问题让哥伦比亚人最担心的问题变得微不足道</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/corruption-dwarfs-every-other-issue-for-colombians-in-new-poll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新民意调查显示，哥伦比亚人对腐败官员的愤怒远甚于国家面临的其他问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/corruption-dwarfs-every-other-issue-for-colombians-in-new-poll</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
